window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Today, I broke that vow. In my defense...I never thought I’d see him again. But when my first night in NYC doesn’t go as planned, I find myself walking into his tattoo shop, the memory of our lost romance still singed on my skin. </p> <p>Brett Jackson is trouble. And I know it. </p> <p>I follow all the rules. He breaks them. </p> <p>He’s forbidden - all wrong for me. </p> <p>I just wish crossing the line with him didn’t feel so right. </p> <p>This newly revised and extended version of the first full-length stand-alone novel in the Manhattan Nights series is a best friend's brother/second-chance romance with humor, suspense, and plenty of heat.</p>"; 
